OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,FMany Jersey charities say they are
OL,7,Fstruggling to stay afloat due to
OL,8,Fdecreasing donations, according to the
OL,9,FChairperson of the island's Charity
OL,10,FAssociation.
OL,12,FMarcus Liddiard explains they are
OL,13,Falready vulnerable as they have not
OL,14,Fyet recovered from the cost of living
OL,15,Fcrisis and the Covid pandemic.
