OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,FHe says the closure of Jersey's
OL,7,FRecovery College and Beresford Street
OL,8,FKitchen scaling back its services
OL,9,Fshows the fall in charitable support
OL,10,Fis "really starting to bite the
OL,11,Findustry".
OL,13,FThe Association of Jersey Charities
OL,14,F(AOJC) ran a survey toward the end of
OL,15,Flast year to see how good causes were
OL,16,Fcoping with the cost of living
OL,17,Fchallenges.
