OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,FOut of 60 respondents, more than half
OL,7,Fsaid that fundraising had dropped in
OL,8,Fthe previous 12 months and around nine
OL,9,Fin ten stated their costs had
OL,10,Fincreased from the same point last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FWith 79% of charities expecting funds
OL,14,Fto drop in the future, Mr Liddiard
OL,15,Fsays residents need to do their part
OL,16,Fto help charities survive.
