OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,FHe explains: "Being a low tax
OL,7,Fjurisdiction, these things aren't
OL,8,Fessentially supported by government,
OL,9,Fthey have to be supported elsewhere,
OL,10,Fand so it comes down to us.
OL,12,F"We can't always look to the
OL,13,Fgovernment and corporate. We have to
OL,14,Flook to all those things, including
OL,15,Findividuals in Jersey, to try and
OL,16,Fstand up for our charities and make
OL,17,FJersey the great place that it is.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
