OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,F"The cost of living challenge means
OL,7,Fthat people have less money to offer
OL,8,Fcharities, so it really is a difficult
OL,9,Ftime, but hopefully Jersey can step up
OL,10,Fto help the charities in their time of
OL,11,Fneed."
OL,13,FThis week, Jersey Post's chairman
OL,14,FKevin Keen took to social media to
OL,15,Fcall on islanders to do more to help
OL,16,Fstruggling charities.
OL,18,FHe says: "In finding excuses to do
OL,19,Fnothing, many of us missed the
OL,20,Fopportunity for us as individuals to
OL,21,Fdo more.
