OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,F"I appreciate that higher interest
OL,7,Frates are making it difficult for some
OL,8,Fbut not all, but most of us could find
OL,9,F#5 or #10 a month to make a monthly
OL,10,Fdonation to a local charity close to
OL,11,Four hearts."
OL,13,FMr Liddiard also pushes back at the
OL,14,Fidea that charities which cannot
OL,15,Fsustain themselves should not be
OL,16,Fsupported.
