OL,3,CJersey charities struggle to cope with
OL,4,Cdecreased donations
OL,6,FHe adds: "Jersey has always been a
OL,7,Ffantastic place for supporting
OL,8,Fcharity. When we've mentioned this
OL,9,Fbefore, people have challenged us
OL,10,Fsaying if charities can't sustain
OL,11,Fthemselves, they don't deserve to
OL,12,Fexist or are there too many charities.
OL,14,F"It's a valid challenge, we need to
OL,15,Fmake sure that all charities are as
OL,16,Fefficient as possible and as
OL,17,Fcollaborative as possible, but I
OL,18,Freally don't think there are too many
OL,19,Fcharities of Jersey.
